{"tid":2252433,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"放寬本地團規定設綠色景點、於旅巴講解 「活現香港」指深度遊難配合、不解政府思維","createTime":"2020-10-21T12:45:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T12:50:38.000Z","uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"204c954254d989fd93689e00039f11e6f5dc0a86","tid":2252433,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T12:45:28.000Z","msg":"政府日前宣布進一步放寬社交限制措施，周五（23 日）起容許旅行社舉辦最多 30 人的本地遊團。舉辦文化導賞團的「活現香港」卻今日於 FB 發文表示，暫未能重開「行街團」，因他們未能符合政府制定的條款，包括行程必須有「綠色景點」、導遊只能於交通工具上講解等，而他們舉辦的深度遊，圍繞早期發展的市區街道，並以步行為主，質疑政府措施傾向傳統「鴨仔團」，未能惠及深度遊旅行團。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%94%BE%E5%AF%AC%E6%9C%AC%E5%9C%B0%E5%9C%98%E8%A6%8F%E5%AE%9A%E8%A8%AD%E7%B6%A0%E8%89%B2%E6%99%AF%E9%BB%9E-%E6%96%BC%E6%97%85%E5%B7%B4%E8%AC%9B%E8%A7%A3-%E6%B4%BB%E7%8F%BE%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF-%E6%8C%87%E6%B7%B1%E5%BA%A6%E9%81%8A%E9%9B%A3%E9%85%8D%E5%90%88-%E4%B8%8D%E8%A7%A3%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%80%9D%E7%B6%AD/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25AF%25AC%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%2598%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%25AE%259A%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E7%25B6%25A0%25E8%2589%25B2%25E6%2599%25AF%25E9%25BB%259E-%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%2597%2585%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25AC%259B%25E8%25A7%25A3-%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E7%258F%25BE%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF-%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%25B7%25B1%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E9%2581%258A%25E9%259B%25A3%25E9%2585%258D%25E5%2590%2588-%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2580%259D%25E7%25B6%25AD%2F&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPZ1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=88b6d4da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E6%2594%25BE%25E5%25AF%25AC%25E6%259C%25AC%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%259C%2598%25E8%25A6%258F%25E5%25AE%259A%25E8%25A8%25AD%25E7%25B6%25A0%25E8%2589%25B2%25E6%2599%25AF%25E9%25BB%259E-%25E6%2596%25BC%25E6%2597%2585%25E5%25B7%25B4%25E8%25AC%259B%25E8%25A7%25A3-%25E6%25B4%25BB%25E7%258F%25BE%25E9%25A6%2599